description: Don't miss out on this recently 2016 New Construction and steps away from the upcoming Washington Village, a future development that will offer a mix of retail, public green space and additional residential units.This is a modern 2bed/2bath + 1 Garage parking unit in a professionally managed building and steps away from Broadway T-Stop And Carson Beach. Unit has a great flow and no wasted square footage + a private balcony. The bright and open layout features surround sound, custom made blinds, fitness center, garage parking and bike storage.
